File Photo
On an important highway of Quetta, shots fired by unknown people killed four policemen including the deputy superintended of police.
Wednesday morning two DSPs, one Sub Inspector and two Constables were on the way to the Police Training Center in a jeep. On Sariab Road near Degree College an unknown rider on a motor cycle attacked the police jeep. He fired continuously. In the attack Sub Inspector Mehdi, Constables Sibgat ul llah and Nasr ul llah died on the spot. DSP Hasan Ali died after reaching the hospital.
